&lt;img alt="MR signal from a line near the center of k-space" src="http://mriquestions.com/uploads/3/4/5/7/34572113/4678104_orig.jpg" style="width: 400px;" /&gt;
&lt;p class="caption"&gt;k空间接近中心行的MR信号幅值高&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;div class="first last figure"&gt;
&lt;img alt="MR signal from a line through periphery of k-space" src="http://mriquestions.com/uploads/3/4/5/7/34572113/7099771_orig.jpg" style="width: 400px;" /&gt;
&lt;p class="caption"&gt;k空间外周行的MR信号幅值低&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
